item.title: Aircraft Model Collection in 2020
item.description: Info: This post covers all my aircraft models which collected in 2020. [Phoenix] Air China B737-800WL, B-5425 “2022 Beijing Olympic Winter Games” Special Colour.

item.title: Aircraft Model Collection in 2018
item.description: Info: This post covers all my aircraft models which collected in 2018. ID photo and basic model information: Order from newest to oldest [Aviation] China Airlines A350-900, B-18918 “Carbon Fibre / Airbus” Special Colour. I flew with her in 2019 from SYD to TPE. Arrived at 2018-12-15. [Phoenix] Cathay Pacific Airways B777-200, B-HNL. The world’s first 777, I flew with her in 2017 from HND to HKG.
